    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specification, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a 6-speed manual Getrag gearbox to a speed-sensitive M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a sophisticated multi-link rear suspension and aluminum control arms for minimized unsprung mass. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp. A definitive example of BMW\u2019s golden era of engineering.",
